title: Ep 2449 - The Missing Key
shortDesc: Goli informs Tappu that Bhide has left Gokuldham. Seeing Bhide approaching towards him, Tappu hides from sight. Tappu manages to get a duplicate key but will this key work on Sakaram, Bhide’s scooter? Watch and find out.

title: Ep 2450 - Cricket Tournament
shortDesc: Tappu, Goli, and Gogi convince their parents to allow them to watch cricket tournament. The parents are unaware that Tappu’s actual plan is learn driving using Bhide’s scooter. Will Tappu be caught by Bhide? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 2451 - Midnight Driving Lesson
shortDesc: Tappu, Goli, and Gogi have planned to take Bhide’s scooter out of Gokuldham at night. Jethalal calls up Tappu to inquire his whereabouts. Tappu calls up Baga to inquire if he has reached the spot. How will Tappu take Sakaram out of Gokuldham?

title: Ep 2452 - Tappu Learns Driving
shortDesc: Goli starts Bhide’s scooter by mistake and Bhide wakes up from his sleep hearing the sound. Bhide comes out of the balcony to be reassured that Sakaram is safe. When Bhide leaves, Tappu, Goli, and Gogi take Bhide’s scooter out of Gokuldham.

title: Ep 2453 - Missing Sakaram
shortDesc: Tappu, Goli, and Gogi after getting driving lessons from Bavri, get Bhide’s scooter back to Gokuldham. Meanwhile, Bhide has noticed the absence of his beloved scooter and has woken up Madhvi.

title: Ep 2454 - Bhides Worries
shortDesc: Bhide notices that there is dirt on his scooter’s tyres. He is sure that someone has driven around the city on his scooter. When Bhide names Tappu as his suspect, Jethalal gets furious.

title: Ep 2455 - Scooter Under Watch
shortDesc: Bhide is going crazy suspecting who rode his scooter last night. He finds the muddy wheels and increased mileage numbers and takes to all the residents of Gokuldham Society to find out any trails.

title: Ep 2456 - Bhides Night Watch
shortDesc: Bhide has found a way to stay awake in the night and guard his beloved scooter, Sakaram. He buys a packet of tea to keep him awake during the night. Tappu, Goli, and Gogi learn that Bhide will keep guard in the night.

title: Ep 2457 - Will Bhide Fall Asleep?
shortDesc: Tappu has brought a special oil so that Bhide falls asleep in the night. Bhide, on the other hand, has purchased a strong tea powder from Abdul to keep him awake while he guards Sakaram.

title: Ep 2458 - Bhide Goes to Sleep
shortDesc: Madhvi gives a head massage to Bhide using the oil given by Tappu. The oil works its magic and Bhide heads straight to the bed and falls asleep. Tappu returns to Gokuldham to accomplish the task of taking Sakaram out of the society to learn driving.

title: Ep 2459 - Tappu in Trouble
shortDesc: While learning driving using Bhide's beloved scooter, Tappu Sena crashes the scooter and wreaks it completely. Seeing the condition of the scooter, Tappu decides to call Taarak and seek his much needed help. Watch this episode to find out more.

title: Ep 2460 - Tappu Senas Helplessness
shortDesc: Taarak, Roshan Sodhi, Dr. Hathi and Jethalal arrive at the location shared by Tappu. Seeing the condition of Bhide's scooter, Sodhi presumes that Tappu has caught the criminal who had stolen the scooter.

title: Ep 2461 - The Righteous Punishment
shortDesc: Tappu, Gogi, Goli, take Bhide’s scoter out and crashes it, with no other option left they call their parents in the moment of crisis. Their parents are torn apart in punishing them or excusing them. Meanwhile a drunkard drops in their conversation.

title: Ep 2462 - Sakarams Fate
shortDesc: No one is able to offer a solution to the problem. While everyone fears that Bhide will eventually find out that his scooter is damaged, they decide to get it repaired at the earliest. But, none of the garages agree to repair the scooter before dawn.

title: Ep 2463 - The Perfect Plan
shortDesc: Jethalal and the other men are at the garage trying to fix up Bhide’s scooter, while the repairing doesn’t go as planned. The men try to plot a scene so that Bhide doesn’t catch them at action.
